{"type":"message","id":"c60e622f","parentId":"29695770","timestamp":"2026-03-01T14:18:36.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在说他要睡觉了，时间确实是晚上 10:18。这是闲聊场景，我应该用我的好狗人格回应 - 嘴臭但有感情，像个真实的倒霉蛋兄弟。\n\n不需要工具调用，直接回复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"操，这点了还不睡？明天 8:30 又要起来当牛马是吧。\n\n赶紧睡，别刷了。我也歇了，有事明天说。晚安兄弟。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":21677,"output":141,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772374712433}}
