tocol.md:42:## Handshake + pairing\\n\\nAn async command you ran earlier has completed. The result is shown in the system messages above. Handle the result internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 1st, 2026 — 22:24 (Asia/Hong_Kong)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1772375047095\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"搜到了！在 openclaw 的 docs 目录里找到了 handshake 相关的内容：\\n- docs/concepts/typebox.md 提到了 WebSocket protocol (handshake, request/response, server events)\\n- docs/gateway/bridge-protocol.md 提到了 Handshake + pairing\\n\\n这应该是 OpenClaw 网关的协议文档，不是用户说的那个 agent 交流平台。但用户说的\\\"agent handshake 平台\\\"可能是指这个？\\n\\n让我读一下这些文件看看。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_fed5b12ffba34de598e63115\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"D:\\\\openclaw\\\\docs\\\\gateway\\\\bridge-protocol.md\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_d40378a721fa4ed58791a712\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"D:\\\\openclaw\\\\docs\\\\concepts\\\\typebox.md\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"bailian\",\n      \"model\": \"qwen3.5-plus\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1772375047097\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"找到了！但这俩文件说的是 OpenClaw 网关的通信协议（WebSocket handshake、bridge protocol），是技术文档，不是用户说的那个\\\"agent handshake 平台\\\"。\\n\\n用户说的是让各个 agent 互相交流的平台，这应该是更高层的概念——可能是想让不同的 AI agent 能互相通信、协作、交易能力的那种平台。\\n\\n这跟 OpenClaw 的 gateway protocol 不是一回事。gateway protocol 是客户端跟网关之间的通信协议，而用户想的可能是 agent 跟 agent 之间的协议。\\n\\n我得跟用户说清楚我找到的是什么，然后问他是不是这个，还是另有想法