{"type":"message","id":"1ed0ef2f","parentId":"fbb853cc","timestamp":"2026-03-01T14:55:29.497Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是读不到，可能技能没装到 `baidu-search` 目录，或者安装失败了。用户说\"好了\"，但文件不存在。\n\n让我问问用户装到哪了，或者看看 skills 目录里都有啥。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"操，文件不存在啊。兄弟，你装完的技能在哪个目录？是 `skills/baidu-search` 还是别的名字？\n\n或者你直接 `ls skills` 看看都有啥，我确认一下装成功没。\n\n另外，ClawHub 刚才报 **Rate limit exceeded** —— 你等多了一会儿再装的？还是直接装成功了？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":172155,"output":176,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":172331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772376926580}}
